So this is basically a reminder to let me remember what sounds are planned and so on.
If the file name ends with -*** that means that anything with the name, a dash and possibly any other characters after that count

name			-	[File][Implement.]	-	Explanation when the sound gets played
————————————————————————————————————————————————————————————————————————————————————————————————————————————————
menu			-	[Draft][Fin]		-	background music in the menu
gamemodeselect	-	[Nope][Fin]			-	background music in the game mode select screen
game-***		-	[Draft][Fin]		-	background music in the game
idrop			-	[Draft][Fin]		-	when a block gets instadropped
drop			-	[Fin][Fin]			-	when a block gets normal-dropped
single			-	[Fin][Fin]			-	one line cleared
double			-	[Fin][Fin]			-	two lines cleared
triple			-	[Fin][Fin]			-	three lines cleared
tetris			-	[Fin][Fin]l			-	four lines cleared
button			-	[Nope][Draft]		-	button gets pressed
move			-	[Nope][Fin]			-	block moves left or right
rotate			-	[Nope][Fin]			-	block rotates
Agameover		-	[Nope][Fin]			-	the game ends [mode A]
Blose			-	[Nope][Fin]			-	player loses [mode B]
Bwin			-	[Nope][Fin]			-	player wins [mode B]
highscore		-	[Nope][Nothing]		-	player gets a highscore [either B or A]
dropdown		-	[Nope][Fin]			-	dropdown expands or contracts
textbox			-	[Nope][Fin]			-	textbox opens or closes
LANwait			-	[Nope][Nothing]		-	waiting for game to start in LAN
LANhost			-	[Nope][Nothing]		-	when 'host in LAN' gets pressed
ONLINEwait		-	[Nope][Nothing]		-	waiting for game to start online
ONLANfirst		-	[Nope][Nothing]		-	when you get 1st place either online or in LAN
ONLANsecond		-	[Nope][Nothing]		-	when you get 2nd place either online or in LAN
ONLANthird		-	[Nope][Nothing]		-	when you get 3rd place either online or in LAN
ONLANlost		-	[Nope][Nothing]		-	when you get 4th place or worse either online or in LAN
ONLANlast		-	[Nope][Nothing]		-	when you get last place (not 1st-3rd place) either online or in LAN
————————————————————————————————————————————————————————————————————————————————————————————————————————————————
